#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/test/Testing.py:56
#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/test/Testing.py:341
msgid ""
"Compares a source image (src_img, which is a vtkImageData) with the saved "
"image file whose name is given in the second argument. If the image file "
"does not exist the image is generated and stored.  If not the source image "
"is compared to that of the figure.  This function also handles multiple "
"images and finds the best matching image."
msgstr ""

